From b9b537c15f74a09e3c5a2aece3ac88441dac147e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 8 May 2025 15:13:01 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: cfg: remove rf_id field
Git-commit: b9b537c15f74a09e3c5a2aece3ac88441dac147e
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

This field is always set for >= 9000 series, but then we
already check that, so it's not needed. Remove it.

Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250508121306.1277801-11-miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
